[{"id": 521921, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4511, "text": "HA meem."}, {"id": 521922, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4512, "text": "UPPENBARELSEN av denna Skrift \u00e4r Guds, den Allsm\u00e4ktiges, den Vises, verk."}, {"id": 521923, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4513, "text": "Vi har inte skapat himlarna och jorden och allt som finns d\u00e4remellan utan en plan och ett syfte och Vi har fastst\u00e4llt en slutpunkt [f\u00f6r allt]. F\u00f6rnekarna av sanningen v\u00e4nder likv\u00e4l ryggen \u00e5t varningarna."}, {"id": 521925, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4514, "text": "S\u00e4g: \"Har ni \u00f6verv\u00e4gt vad det \u00e4r ni anropar i Guds st\u00e4lle? Visa Mig vad dessa [v\u00e4sen eller makter] har skapat p\u00e5 jorden! Eller hade de del i himlarnas [skapelse]? Visa upp en Skrift som uppenbarats f\u00f6re denna eller vad som kan ha bevarats av [\u00e4ldre sl\u00e4ktens] kunskap [och som ni st\u00f6der er p\u00e5], om ni talar sanning!\""}, {"id": 521926, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 502, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4515, "text": "Och vem beg\u00e5r ett st\u00f6rre misstag \u00e4n den som i Guds st\u00e4lle anropar dem, som inte kan svara honom f\u00f6rr\u00e4n p\u00e5 Uppst\u00e5ndelsens dag och som inte ens \u00e4r medvetna om att de anropas"}, {"id": 521927, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4516, "text": "N\u00e4r m\u00e4nniskorna samlas [inf\u00f6r Domen] skall de bli [sina tillbedjares] fiender och ta avst\u00e5nd fr\u00e5n deras dyrkan."}, {"id": 521928, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4517, "text": "N\u00e4r V\u00e5ra klara budskap l\u00e4ses upp f\u00f6r dem, s\u00e4ger de om sanningen som de f\u00e5r h\u00f6ra: \"Detta \u00e4r uppenbart bl\u00e4ndande och f\u00f6rh\u00e4xande v\u00e4ltalighet.\""}, {"id": 521929, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4518, "text": "Eller ocks\u00e5 s\u00e4ger de: \"Det \u00e4r han [sj\u00e4lv] som har f\u00f6rfattat det!\" S\u00e4g [Muhammad]: \"Om jag hade f\u00f6rfattat den hade ni inte kunnat skydda mig mot Gud. Han har full vetskap om den str\u00f6m [av f\u00f6rtal] som fl\u00f6dar \u00f6ver era l\u00e4ppar; inga [andra] vittnen \u00e4n Han beh\u00f6vs mellan mig och er. Han \u00e4r Den som st\u00e4ndigt f\u00f6rl\u00e5ter, Den som st\u00e4ndigt visar barmh\u00e4rtighet.\""}, {"id": 521930, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4519, "text": "S\u00e4g: \"Jag \u00e4r inte den f\u00f6rste av [Guds] s\u00e4ndebud och jag vet inte vad som skall ske med mig och med er. Jag f\u00f6ljer bara det som uppenbaras f\u00f6r mig; jag \u00e4r ingenting annat \u00e4n en varnare, [som varnar] klart och entydigt.\""}, {"id": 521931, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 438, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4520, "text": "S\u00e4g: \"Hur ser ni [p\u00e5 detta]? Om det [som jag f\u00f6rkunnar verkligen] kommer fr\u00e5n Gud och ni f\u00f6rnekar det, [har ni inte d\u00e5 gjort or\u00e4tt]? Ett vittne bland Israels barn vittnade ju att en [som \u00e4r] honom lik [skall komma] och [vittnet] trodde [p\u00e5 detta], men ni i ert h\u00f6gmod [avvisar det]! Gud v\u00e4gleder sannerligen inte dem som g\u00f6r or\u00e4tt!\""}, {"id": 521932, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4521, "text": "Och f\u00f6rnekarna av sanningen s\u00e4ger om dem som blivit troende: \"Hade det funnits n\u00e5got gott [i detta budskap] skulle inte dessa [el\u00e4ndiga stackare] haft s\u00e5 br\u00e5ttom att anta det f\u00f6re oss.\" Och n\u00e4r de inte vill l\u00e5ta sig ledas av det, s\u00e4ger de: \"Allt detta \u00e4r [bara] gamla l\u00f6gner.\""}, {"id": 521933, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4522, "text": "Denna [Koran] f\u00f6regicks av den Skrift som uppenbarades f\u00f6r Moses som en v\u00e4gvisare och en [k\u00e4lla till] n\u00e5d; och detta \u00e4r en uppenbarelse som p\u00e5 det arabiska spr\u00e5ket bekr\u00e4ftar [den f\u00f6reg\u00e5ende] och som varnar de or\u00e4ttf\u00e4rdiga och ger dem som g\u00f6r det goda och det r\u00e4tta ett hoppets budskap."}, {"id": 521934, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4523, "text": "De som bek\u00e4nner \"Gud \u00e4r v\u00e5r Herre\" och s\u00e5 h\u00e5ller fast [vid detta] skall inte k\u00e4nna fruktan och ingen sorg skall tynga dem."}, {"id": 521935, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 503, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4524, "text": "De har paradiset till arvedel och d\u00e4r skall de f\u00f6rbli till evig tid - l\u00f6nen f\u00f6r deras handlingar!"}, {"id": 521936, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4525, "text": "VI HAR f\u00f6rmanat m\u00e4nniskan att visa godhet mot sina f\u00f6r\u00e4ldrar. [Den blivande] modern b\u00e4r sin b\u00f6rda med m\u00f6da och med sm\u00e4rta f\u00f6der hon - ja, [hennes m\u00f6da] varar trettio m\u00e5nader, amningstiden [inbegripen] Och n\u00e4r m\u00e4nniskan vid det fyrtionde levnads\u00e5ret n\u00e5r sin fulla mognad, ber hon: \"Herre! G\u00f6r att jag [alltid] visar tacksamhet mot Dig f\u00f6r Dina v\u00e4lg\u00e4rningar mot mig och mot mina f\u00f6r\u00e4ldrar och att jag g\u00f6r det goda och det r\u00e4tta och allt det som Du ser med v\u00e4lbehag; och g\u00f6r mina efterkommande till goda och r\u00e4ttr\u00e5diga m\u00e4nniskor! Jag \u00e4r en av dem som har underkastat sig Din vilja och som [alltid] v\u00e4nder \u00e5ter till Dig i \u00e5nger.\""}, {"id": 521937, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4526, "text": "Av vad s\u00e5dana [m\u00e4nniskor] gjort skall Vi tillgodor\u00e4kna dem det b\u00e4sta och Vi skall \u00f6verse med deras d\u00e5liga handlingar; [ja, de skall vara] bland paradisets arvtagare enligt det sanna l\u00f6fte som de har f\u00e5tt [genom profeterna]."}, {"id": 521938, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4527, "text": "Det finns den som svarar sina f\u00f6r\u00e4ldrar [n\u00e4r de uppmanar honom att tro]: \"Sk\u00e4ms ni inte? Mig lovar ni att jag skall uppv\u00e4ckas [fr\u00e5n de d\u00f6da] - men [ni tiger om alla] de sl\u00e4ktled som har g\u00e5tt f\u00f6re mig?\" [F\u00f6r\u00e4ldrarna] ber om Guds hj\u00e4lp [och s\u00e4ger till sonen]: \"Du drar olycka \u00f6ver dig! Antag tron! Guds l\u00f6fte \u00e4r sanning!\" Men han svarar: \"Det d\u00e4r \u00e4r bara sagor fr\u00e5n f\u00f6rf\u00e4dernas tid!\""}, {"id": 521939, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4528, "text": "Och \u00f6ver [s\u00e5dana som] denne skall samma dom osvikligt f\u00e4llas som den som f\u00e4lldes \u00f6ver tidigare sl\u00e4kten av osynliga v\u00e4sen och m\u00e4nniskor; ja, de kommer att h\u00f6ra till f\u00f6rlorarna!"}, {"id": 521940, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4529, "text": "Och f\u00f6r var och en skall det finnas grader efter vad han har gjort [av gott eller ont], s\u00e5 att [Gud p\u00e5 denna grund] skall ge dem full l\u00f6n f\u00f6r deras handlingar och ingen skall tillfogas or\u00e4tt."}, {"id": 521941, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 504, "ruku": 439, "hizb_quarter": 201, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4530, "text": "Och den Dag d\u00e5 f\u00f6rnekarna av sanningen f\u00f6rs fram inf\u00f6r Elden [skall Vi s\u00e4ga till dem:] \"Ni har f\u00f6rsl\u00f6sat det goda som livet erbj\u00f6d er och njutit det [utan en tanke p\u00e5 evigheten]; i dag drabbar er straffet med skam och van\u00e4ra d\u00e4rf\u00f6r att ni upptr\u00e4dde med h\u00f6gmod p\u00e5 jorden utan fog och d\u00e4rf\u00f6r att ni st\u00e4ndigt trotsade [V\u00e5ra befallningar].\""}, {"id": 521943, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4531, "text": "OCH MINNS hur [stammen] Aads broder - sedan [m\u00e5nga] varnare passerat som han hade k\u00e4nnedom om och andra om vilka han var okunnig - varnade sitt folk [som levde] i sanddynernas land: \"Dyrka ingen utom Gud! Jag fruktar det straff [som annars kommer att drabba] er en olycksdiger Dag!\""}, {"id": 521944, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4532, "text": "De svarade: \"Har du kommit f\u00f6r att f\u00f6rm\u00e5 oss att \u00f6verge v\u00e5ra gudar? L\u00e5t d\u00e5 det som du hotar oss med drabba oss, om du talar sanning!\""}, {"id": 521945, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4533, "text": "Han sade: \"Gud ensam har kunskap [om det straff som skall drabba er]. Jag framf\u00f6r [bara] till er det [budskap] som jag har anf\u00f6rtrotts. Men jag ser att ni \u00e4r d\u00e5raktiga och okunniga m\u00e4nniskor.\""}, {"id": 521946, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4534, "text": "Och n\u00e4r de s\u00e5g [straffet som] en molnbank [vid horisonten] som r\u00f6rde sig i riktning mot deras dalar, ropade de [glatt]: \"Se, ett moln! Det skall ge oss regn!\" [Hud sade:] \"Nej, detta \u00e4r straffet som ni s\u00e5 ot\u00e5ligt bad om: en stormvind som f\u00f6r med sig sv\u00e5rt lidande"}, {"id": 521947, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4535, "text": "och som skall \u00f6del\u00e4gga allt enligt sin Herres befallning.\" Och n\u00e4r morgonen kom, kunde ingenting urskiljas annat \u00e4n [resterna av] deras bost\u00e4der. S\u00e5 l\u00f6nar Vi de obotf\u00e4rdiga syndarna."}, {"id": 521948, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 440, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4536, "text": "Vi hade sk\u00e4nkt dem en b\u00e4ttre och s\u00e4krare plats p\u00e5 jorden \u00e4n den som Vi har gett er, och Vi hade beg\u00e5vat dem med h\u00f6rsel, syn och f\u00f6rst\u00e5nd. Men varken deras h\u00f6rsel eller deras syn eller deras f\u00f6rst\u00e5nd var dem till n\u00e5gon nytta - de framh\u00e4rdade i att f\u00f6rneka Guds budskap - och s\u00e5 inringades de av det som varit f\u00f6rem\u00e5l f\u00f6r deras h\u00e5n och sk\u00e4mt."}, {"id": 521949, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4537, "text": "Vi har l\u00e5tit m\u00e5nga folk [som levde] i er n\u00e4rhet g\u00e5 under, trots att Vi p\u00e5 m\u00e5nga s\u00e4tt hade f\u00f6rtydligat budskapen [och varningarna] f\u00f6r att f\u00f6rm\u00e5 dem att [t\u00e4nka sig f\u00f6r och] v\u00e4nda om."}, {"id": 521950, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 505, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4538, "text": "Varf\u00f6r fick de ingen hj\u00e4lp av dem som de tillbad som gudomligheter vid sidan av Gud f\u00f6r att de skulle f\u00f6ra dem n\u00e4rmare [Honom]? Nej, [i n\u00f6dens stund] \u00f6vergav [gudarna] dem; det var ju bara en historia som de hade ljugit ihop."}, {"id": 521951, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4539, "text": "OCH SE, Vi l\u00e4t en liten skara av osynliga v\u00e4sen n\u00e4rma sig dig [Muhammad], s\u00e5 att de kunde h\u00f6ra [dig l\u00e4sa ur] Koranen, och n\u00e4r de kom fram, sade de [till varandra]: \"Lyssna nu noga!\" Och n\u00e4r l\u00e4sningen var slut, v\u00e4nde de tillbaka till de sina som varnare"}, {"id": 521952, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4540, "text": "och sade: \"Landsm\u00e4n! Vi har lyssnat till en uppenbarelse, som [m\u00e4nniskorna] efter Moses [tid] har f\u00e5tt del av och som bekr\u00e4ftar det som \u00e4nnu best\u00e5r [av \u00e4ldre tiders uppenbarelser] och den leder [lyssnaren] till sanningen och till en rak v\u00e4g."}, {"id": 521953, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4541, "text": "Landsm\u00e4n! H\u00f6r den som kallar er till Gud och tro p\u00e5 honom! [Gud] skall ge er f\u00f6rl\u00e5telse f\u00f6r era synder och skona er fr\u00e5n ett pl\u00e5gsamt straff."}, {"id": 521954, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4542, "text": "Men den som inte lyssnar till honom kan inte trotsa [Guds vilja] p\u00e5 jorden och han kommer inte att finna en annan beskyddare \u00e4n Gud. Det \u00e4r uppenbart att den [m\u00e4nniskan] har g\u00e5tt vilse.\""}, {"id": 521955, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4543, "text": "F\u00d6RST\u00c5R de inte att Gud, som har skapat himlarna och jorden utan att skapelsen av dem tr\u00f6ttade Honom, har makt att \u00e5teruppv\u00e4cka de d\u00f6da? Ja, Han har allt i Sin makt!"}, {"id": 521956, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4544, "text": "Och den Dag d\u00e5 f\u00f6rnekarna av sanningen skall f\u00f6ras fram inf\u00f6r Elden, [skall de tillfr\u00e5gas:] \"\u00c4r detta inte verklighet?\" [Och] de skall svara: \"Vid v\u00e5r Herre! Helt visst \u00e4r det [verklighet]!\" [Och Gud] skall s\u00e4ga: \"Smaka d\u00e5 straffet f\u00f6r er f\u00f6rnekelse av sanningen!\""}, {"id": 521957, "identifier": "sv.bernstrom", "surah_number": 46, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u062d\u0642\u0627\u0641", "surah_en_name": "Al-Ahqaf", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Dunes", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 26, "manzil": 6, "page": 506, "ruku": 441, "hizb_quarter": 202, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "sv", "name": "Bernstr\u00f6m", "transelator_en_name": "Knut Bernstr\u00f6m", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 4545, "text": "B\u00c4R [Muhammad, motg\u00e5ng och of\u00f6rr\u00e4tt] med t\u00e5lamod, liksom s\u00e4ndebuden [f\u00f6re dig] - m\u00e4n, fasta i sina f\u00f6resatser - bar [allt] med t\u00e5lamod; och beg\u00e4r inte att f\u00f6rnekarna genast skall [straffas]! Den Dag d\u00e5 de med egna \u00f6gon f\u00e5r se det som lovats dem, [kommer det att f\u00f6refalla dem] som om de inte hade tillbringat mer \u00e4n en timme av en dag p\u00e5 jorden. [Detta \u00e4r] budskapet. Kommer d\u00e5 n\u00e5gon att f\u00f6rg\u00f6ras utom de som f\u00f6rh\u00e4rdade sig i synd och trots [mot Gud]?"}]